OL,3,CSinger Britney Spears arrested in
OL,4,CCalifornia
OL,6,FAmerican pop star Britney Spears has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested in California.
OL,9,FArrest details on Ventura County
OL,10,FSheriff's website say the singer was
OL,11,Farrested at 9:28pm on March 4, and
OL,12,Fbooked five and a half hours later at
OL,13,F3 am on March 5.
OL,15,FThe singer was released at 6 am that
OL,16,Fmorning and a court date has been set
OL,17,Fat Ventura County Superior Court for
OL,18,FMay 4.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
