OL,3,CSinger Britney Spears arrested in
OL,4,CCalifornia
OL,6,FThe arrest details do not list the
OL,7,Freason for arrest, but do state her
OL,8,Fvehicle as having been towed.
OL,10,FSpears' arrest comes after reports the
OL,11,Fsinger had just been granted a
OL,12,Frestraining order against a man from
OL,13,FLouisiana who is alleged to have
OL,14,Fharassed her since 2013.
