OL,3,CSinger Britney Spears arrested in
OL,4,CCalifornia
OL,6,FWednesday's arrest is not the singer's
OL,7,Ffirst run-in with the law, having
OL,8,Fpreviously been arrested in 2007, for
OL,9,Fcharges including an alleged hit-and-
OL,10,Frun with a parked car in Los Angeles.
OL,11,FThe charges were eventually dropped
OL,12,Fafter Spears paid damages to the car's
OL,13,Fowner.
OL,15,FIn early 2024 the singer vowed to
OL,16,Fnever return to the music industry
OL,17,Fafter securing financial independence
OL,18,Ffrom a restrictive conservatorship
OL,19,Fcontrolled by her father.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
